INSERT INTO `chat_history` VALUES (342883463518060544, '我将为您创建一个锻炼助手单页网站，包含锻炼计划展示、计时器和进度跟踪功能。\n\n```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>健身助手 - 您的个人锻炼伙伴</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"style.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header class=\"header\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1 class=\"logo\">🏋️‍♂️ 健身助手</h1>\n            <nav class=\"nav\">\n                <ul>\n                    <li><a href=\"#home\" class=\"nav-link active\">首页</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#workouts\" class=\"nav-link\">锻炼计划</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#timer\" class=\"nav-link\">计时器</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#progress\" class=\"nav-link\">进度跟踪</a></li>\n                </ul>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <main class=\"main\">\n        <!-- 首页部分 -->\n        <section id=\"home\" class=\"section active\">\n            <div class=\"hero\">\n                <div class=\"container\">\n                    <h2>开始您的健身之旅</h2>\n                    <p>专业的锻炼计划，智能的计时功能，完整的进度跟踪</p>\n                    <button class=\"cta-button\" onclick=\"showSection(\'workouts\')\">开始锻炼</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <!-- 锻炼计划部分 -->\n        <section id=\"workouts\" class=\"section\">\n            <div class=\"container\">\n                <h2>推荐锻炼计划</h2>\n                <div class=\"workout-grid\">\n                    <div class=\"workout-card\">\n                        <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/300/200?random=1\" alt=\"力量训练\">\n                        <h3>力量训练</h3>\n                        <p>增强肌肉力量和耐力</p>\n                        <ul>\n                            <li>深蹲: 3组 x 12次</li>\n                            <li>卧推: 3组 x 10次</li>\n                            <li>硬拉: 3组 x 8次</li>\n                        </ul>\n                        <button class=\"start-workout\" data-workout=\"力量训练\">开始训练</button>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"workout-card\">\n                        <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/300/200?random=2\" alt=\"有氧训练\">\n                        <h3>有氧训练</h3>\n                        <p>提高心肺功能和燃脂</p>\n                        <ul>\n                            <li>跑步: 30分钟</li>\n                            <li>跳绳: 5组 x 1分钟</li>\n                            <li>高抬腿: 4组 x 45秒</li>\n                        </ul>\n                        <button class=\"start-workout\" data-workout=\"有氧训练\">开始训练</button>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"workout-card\">\n                        <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/300/200?random=3\" alt=\"核心训练\">\n                        <h3>核心训练</h3>\n                        <p>强化核心肌群</p>\n                        <ul>\n                            <li>平板支撑: 3组 x 60秒</li>\n                            <li>仰卧起坐: 3组 x 20次</li>\n                            <li>俄罗斯转体: 3组 x 15次</li>\n                        </ul>\n                        <button class=\"start-workout\" data-workout=\"核心训练\">开始训练</button>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <!-- 计时器部分 -->\n        <section id=\"timer\" class=\"section\">\n            <div class=\"container\">\n                <h2>锻炼计时器</h2>\n                <div class=\"timer-container\">\n                    <div class=\"timer-display\">\n                        <span id=\"minutes\">25</span>:<span id=\"seconds\">00</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"timer-controls\">\n                        <button id=\"start-timer\" class=\"timer-btn\">开始</button>\n                        <button id=\"pause-timer\" class=\"timer-btn\">暂停</button>\n                        <button id=\"reset-timer\" class=\"timer-btn\">重置</button>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"timer-settings\">\n                        <label for=\"work-duration\">锻炼时间 (分钟):</label>\n                        <input type=\"number\" id=\"work-duration\" min=\"1\" max=\"60\" value=\"25\">\n                        <label for=\"rest-duration\">休息时间 (分钟):</label>\n                        <input type=\"number\" id=\"rest-duration\" min=\"1\" max=\"15\" value=\"5\">\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <!-- 进度跟踪部分 -->\n        <section id=\"progress\" class=\"section\">\n            <div class=\"container\">\n                <h2>进度跟踪</h2>\n                <div class=\"progress-stats\">\n                    <div class=\"stat-card\">\n                        <h3>本周锻炼</h3>\n                        <p class=\"stat-number\" id=\"weekly-workouts\">0</p>\n                        <p>次</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"stat-card\">\n                        <h3>总时长</h3>\n                        <p class=\"stat-number\" id=\"total-minutes\">0</p>\n                        <p>分钟</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"stat-card\">\n                        <h3>完成计划</h3>\n                        <p class=\"stat-number\" id=\"completed-workouts\">0</p>\n                        <p>个</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"workout-history\">\n                    <h3>最近锻炼记录</h3>\n                    <ul id=\"workout-history-list\">\n                        <!-- 锻炼记录将通过JS动态添加 -->\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <button id=\"clear-progress\" class=\"clear-btn\">清除进度</button>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer class=\"footer\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2024 健身助手 - 让锻炼更简单</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script src=\"script.js\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\n```css\n/* 重置和基础样式 */\n* {\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 0;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n}\n\nbody {\n    font-family: \'Arial\', sans-serif;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    color: #333;\n    background-color: #f8f9fa;\n}\n\n.container {\n    max-width: 1200px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    padding: 0 20px;\n}\n\n/* 头部导航 */\n.header {\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n    color: white;\n    padding: 1rem 0;\n    position: sticky;\n    top: 0;\n    z-index: 100;\n}\n\n.header .container {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n}\n\n.logo {\n    font-size: 1.5rem;\n    font-weight: bold;\n}\n\n.nav ul {\n    display: flex;\n    list-style: none;\n    gap: 2rem;\n}\n\n.nav-link {\n    color: white;\n    text-decoration: none;\n    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;\n    border-radius: 5px;\n    transition: background-color 0.3s;\n}\n\n.nav-link:hover,\n.nav-link.active {\n    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n}\n\n/* 主要内容区域 */\n.main {\n    min-height: calc(100vh - 140px);\n}\n\n.section {\n    display: none;\n    padding: 2rem 0;\n}\n\n.section.active {\n    display: block;\n}\n\n/* 首页英雄区域 */\n.hero {\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n    color: white;\n    text-align: center;\n    padding: 4rem 0;\n}\n\n.hero h2 {\n    font-size: 3rem;\n    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n}\n\n.hero p {\n    font-size: 1.2rem;\n    margin-bottom: 2rem;\n    opacity: 0.9;\n}\n\n.cta-button {\n    background: #ff6b6b;\n    color: white;\n    border: none;\n    padding: 1rem 2rem;\n    font-size: 1.1rem;\n    border-radius: 50px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: transform 0.3s, background-color 0.3s;\n}\n\n.cta-button:hover {\n    transform: translateY(-2px);\n    background: #ff5252;\n}\n\n/* 锻炼计划网格 */\n.workout-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n    gap: 2rem;\n    margin-top: 2rem;\n}\n\n.workout-card {\n    background: white;\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n    transition: transform 0.3s;\n}\n\n.workout-card:hover {\n    transform: translateY(-5px);\n}\n\n.workout-card img {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 200px;\n    object-fit: cover;\n}\n\n.workout-card h3 {\n    padding: 1rem;\n    font-size: 1.5rem;\n    color: #333;\n}\n\n.workout-card p {\n    padding: 0 1rem;\n    color: #666;\n}\n\n.workout-card ul {\n    padding: 1rem;\n    list-style: none;\n}\n\n.workout-card li {\n    padding: 0.5rem 0;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;\n}\n\n.workout-card li:last-child {\n    border-bottom: none;\n}\n\n.start-workout {\n    width: 100%;\n    background: #667eea;\n    color: white;\n    border: none;\n    padding: 1rem;\n    font-size: 1rem;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: background-color 0.3s;\n}\n\n.start-workout:hover {\n    background: #5a6fd8;\n}\n\n/* 计时器样式 */\n.timer-container {\n    background: white;\n    padding: 2rem;\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n    text-align: center;\n    max-width: 500px;\n    margin: 2rem auto;\n}\n\n.timer-display {\n    font-size: 4rem;\n    font-weight: bold;\n    color: #667eea;\n    margin-bottom: 2rem;\n}\n\n.timer-controls {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 1rem;\n    justify-content: center;\n    margin-bottom: 2rem;\n}\n\n.timer-btn {\n    background: #667eea;\n    color: white;\n    border: none;\n    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;\n    border-radius: 5px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: background-color 0.3s;\n}\n\n.timer-btn:hover {\n    background: #5a6fd8;\n}\n\n.timer-settings {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n    gap: 1rem;\n    text-align: left;\n}\n\n.timer-settings label {\n    font-weight: bold;\n    color: #666;\n}\n\n.timer-settings input {\n    padding: 0.5rem;\n    border: 1px solid #ddd;\n    border-radius: 5px;\n    width: 100%;\n}\n\n/* 进度跟踪样式 */\n.progress-stats {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));\n    gap: 2rem;\n    margin-bottom: 3rem;\n}\n\n.stat-card {\n    background: white;\n    padding: 2rem;\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n    text-align: center;\n}\n\n.stat-number {\n    font-size: 3rem;\n    font-weight: bold;\n    color: #667eea;\n    margin: 1rem 0;\n}\n\n.workout-history {\n    background: white;\n    padding: 2rem;\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n    margin-bottom: 2rem;\n}\n\n.workout-history h3 {\n    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n    color: #333;\n}\n\n.workout-history ul {\n    list-style: none;\n}\n\n.workout-history li {\n    padding: 1rem;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n}\n\n.workout-history li:last-child {\n    border-bottom: none;\n}\n\n.clear-btn {\n    background: #ff6b6b;\n    color: white;\n    border: none;\n    padding: 1rem 2rem;\n    border-radius: 5px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: background-color 0.3s;\n}\n\n.clear-btn:hover {\n    background: #ff5252;\n}\n\n/* 页脚 */\n.footer {\n    background: #333;\n    color: white;\n    text-align: center;\n    padding: 2rem 0;\n}\n\n/* 响应式设计 */\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .header .container {\n        flex-direction: column;\n        gap: 1rem;\n    }\n\n    .nav ul {\n        gap: 1rem;\n    }\n\n    .hero h2 {\n        font-size: 2rem;\n    }\n\n    .timer-display {\n        font-size: 3rem;\n    }\n\n    .timer-controls {\n        flex-direction: column;\n        align-items: center;\n    }\n\n    .timer-settings {\n        grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    }\n\n    .workout-grid {\n        grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    }\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 480px) {\n    .container {\n        padding: 0 10px;\n    }\n\n    .hero {\n        padding: 2rem 0;\n    }\n\n    .timer-display {\n        font-size: 2.5rem;\n    }\n\n    .stat-number {\n        font-size: 2rem;\n    }\n}\n```\n\n```javascript\n// 全局变量\nlet timerInterval;\nlet isTimerRunning = false;\nlet totalSeconds = 25 * 60; // 默认25分钟\nlet isWorkTime = true;\n\n// 进度数据\nlet progressData = {\n    weeklyWorkouts: 0,\n    totalMinutes: 0,\n    completedWorkouts: 0,\n    workoutHistory: []\n};\n\n// DOM 加载完成后初始化\ndocument.addEventListener(\'DOMContentLoaded\', function() {\n    initializeApp();\n    setupEventListeners();\n    loadProgressData();\n});\n\n// 初始化应用\nfunction initializeApp() {\n    updateTimerDisplay();\n    updateProgressStats();\n}\n\n// 设置事件监听器\nfunction setupEventListeners() {\n    // 导航链接点击事件\n    const navLinks = document.querySelectorAll(\'.nav-link\');\n    navLinks.forEach(link => {\n        link.addEventListener(\'click\', function(e) {\n            e.preventDefault();\n            const targetSection = this.getAttribute(\'href\').substring(1);\n            showSection(targetSection);\n            \n            // 更新活跃导航链接\n            navLinks.forEach(l => l.classList.remove(\'active\'));\n            this.classList.add(\'active\');\n        });\n    });\n\n    // 开始锻炼按钮\n    const startWorkoutButtons = document.querySelectorAll(\'.start-workout\');\n    startWorkoutButtons.forEach(button => {\n        button.addEventListener(\'click\', function() {\n            const workoutType = this.getAttribute(\'data-workout\');\n            startWorkout(workoutType);\n        });\n    });\n\n    // 计时器控制按钮\n    document.getElementById(\'start-timer\').addEventListener(\'click\', startTimer);\n    document.getElementById(\'pause-timer\').addEventListener(\'click\', pauseTimer);\n    document.getElementById(\'reset-timer\').addEventListener(\'click\', resetTimer);\n\n    // 计时器设置输入\n    document.getElementById(\'work-duration\').addEventListener(\'change\', updateTimerSettings);\n    document.getElementById(\'rest-duration\').addEventListener(\'change\', updateTimerSettings);\n\n    // 清除进度按钮\n    document.getElementById(\'clear-progress\').addEventListener(\'click\', clearProgress);\n}\n\n// 显示指定部分\nfunction showSection(sectionId) {\n    // 隐藏所有部分\n    const sections = document.querySelectorAll(\'.section\');\n    sections.forEach(section => {\n        section.classList.remove(\'active\');\n    });\n\n    // 显示目标部分\n    const targetSection = document.getElementById(sectionId);\n    if (targetSection) {\n        targetSection.classList.add(\'active\');\n    }\n}\n\n// 开始锻炼\nfunction startWorkout(workoutType) {\n    // 切换到计时器部分\n    showSection(\'timer\');\n    \n    // 更新导航活跃状态\n    const navLinks = document.querySelectorAll(\'.nav-link\');\n    navLinks.forEach(link => link.classList.remove(\'active\'));\n    document.querySelector(`[href=\"#timer\"]`).classList.add(\'active\');\n    \n    // 记录锻炼开始\n    const workoutRecord = {\n        type: workoutType,\n        startTime: new Date().toLocaleString(),\n        duration: 0\n    };\n    \n    progressData.workoutHistory.unshift(workoutRecord);\n    \n    // 更新进度数据\n    progressData.weeklyWorkouts++;\n    progressData.completedWorkouts++;\n    \n    // 保存数据并更新显示\n    saveProgressData();\n    updateProgressStats();\n    \n    alert(`开始 ${workoutType} 训练！计时器已准备就绪。`);\n}\n\n// 计时器功能\nfunction startTimer() {\n    if (!isTimerRunning) {\n        isTimerRunning = true;\n        timerInterval = setInterval(updateTimer, 1000);\n        document.getElementById(\'start-timer\').textContent = \'继续\';\n    }\n}\n\nfunction pauseTimer() {\n    isTimerRunning = false;\n    clearInterval(timerInterval);\n}\n\nfunction resetTimer() {\n    pauseTimer();\n    isWorkTime = true;\n    const workMinutes = parseInt(document.getElementById(\'work-duration\').value);\n    totalSeconds = workMinutes * 60;\n    updateTimerDisplay();\n    document.getElementById(\'start-timer\').textContent = \'开始\';\n}\n\nfunction updateTimer() {\n    if (totalSeconds > 0) {\n        totalSeconds--;\n        updateTimerDisplay();\n    } else {\n        // 时间到，切换工作/休息时间\n        clearInterval(timerInterval);\n        isTimerRunning = false;\n        \n        if (isWorkTime) {\n            // 工作时间结束，切换到休息时间\n            isWorkTime = false;\n            const restMinutes = parseInt(document.getElementById(\'rest-duration\').value);\n            totalSeconds = restMinutes * 60;\n            alert(\'锻炼时间结束！开始休息时间。\');\n        } else {\n            // 休息时间结束，切换到工作时间\n            isWorkTime = true;\n            const workMinutes = parseInt(document.getElementById(\'work-duration\').value);\n            totalSeconds = workMinutes * 60;\n            alert(\'休息时间结束！开始新的锻炼周期。\');\n            \n            // 记录完成的锻炼时间\n            progressData.totalMinutes += parseInt(document.getElementById(\'work-duration\').value);\n            saveProgressData();\n            updateProgressStats();\n        }\n        \n        updateTimerDisplay();\n        document.getElementById(\'start-timer\').textContent = \'开始\';\n    }\n}\n\nfunction updateTimerDisplay() {\n    const minutes = Math.floor(totalSeconds / 60);\n    const seconds = totalSeconds % 60;\n    \n    document.getElementById(\'minutes\').textContent = minutes.toString().padStart(2, \'0\');\n    document.getElementById(\'seconds\').textContent = seconds.toString().padStart(2, \'0\');\n    \n    // 根据工作/休息时间改变颜色\n    const timerDisplay = document.querySelector(\'.timer-display\');\n    if (isWorkTime) {\n        timerDisplay.style.color = \'#667eea\'; // 蓝色 - 工作时间\n    } else {\n        timerDisplay.style.color = \'#ff6b6b\'; // 红色 - 休息时间\n    }\n}\n\nfunction updateTimerSettings() {\n    if (!isTimerRunning) {\n        const workMinutes = parseInt(document.getElementById(\'work-duration\').value);\n        if (isWorkTime) {\n            totalSeconds = workMinutes * 60;\n        }\n        updateTimerDisplay();\n    }\n}\n\n// 进度跟踪功能\nfunction updateProgressStats() {\n    document.getElementById(\'weekly-workouts\').textContent = progressData.weeklyWorkouts;\n    document.getElementById(\'total-minutes\').textContent = progressData.totalMinutes;\n    document.getElementById(\'completed-workouts\').textContent = progressData.completedWorkouts;\n    \n    // 更新锻炼历史\n    const historyList = document.getElementById(\'workout-history-list\');\n    historyList.innerHTML = \'\';\n    \n    progressData.workoutHistory.slice(0, 5).forEach(record => {\n        const listItem = document.createElement(\'li\');\n        listItem.innerHTML = `\n            <span>${record.type}</span>\n            <span>${record.startTime}</span>\n        `;\n        historyList.appendChild(listItem);\n    });\n}\n\nfunction clearProgress() {\n    if (confirm(\'确定要清除所有进度数据吗？此操作不可撤销。\')) {\n        progressData = {\n            weeklyWorkouts: 0,\n            totalMinutes: 0,\n            completedWorkouts: 0,\n            workoutHistory: []\n        };\n        saveProgressData();\n        updateProgressStats();\n        alert(\'进度数据已清除！\');\n    }\n}\n\n// 本地存储功能\nfunction saveProgressData() {\n    localStorage.setItem(\'fitnessAssistantProgress\', JSON.stringify(progressData));\n}\n\nfunction loadProgressData() {\n    const savedData = localStorage.getItem(\'fitnessAssistantProgress\');\n    if (savedData) {\n        progressData = JSON.parse(savedData);\n        updateProgressStats();\n    }\n}\n\n// 每周重置周锻炼次数（简化实现）\nfunction resetWeeklyStats() {\n    progressData.weeklyWorkouts = 0;\n    saveProgressData();\n    updateProgressStats();\n}\n\n// 模拟每周重置（实际应用中应该基于真实时间）\nsetInterval(resetWeeklyStats, 7 * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000); // 7天\n```\n\n## 功能说明\n\n这个锻炼助手小程序包含以下核心功能：\n\n### 🏠 首页\n- 欢迎界面和快速开始按钮\n\n### 💪 锻炼计划\n- 三种预设训练计划：力量训练、有氧训练、核心训练\n- 每个计划包含具体的训练项目和组数\n- 一键开始训练功能\n\n### ⏱️ 计时器\n- 可自定义的工作时间和休息时间\n- 开始、暂停、重置控制\n- 工作/休息时间自动切换\n- 视觉反馈（颜色变化）\n\n### 📊 进度跟踪\n- 本周锻炼次数统计\n- 总锻炼时长记录\n- 完成计划数量\n- 最近锻炼历史\n- 数据本地存储\n\n### 🎯 特色功能\n- 完全响应式设计，适配各种设备\n- 本地存储，数据不会丢失\n- 直观的用户界面和流畅的交互\n- 无需外部依赖，纯原生实现\n\n用户可以通过导航在不同功能间切换，开始锻炼时会自动跳转到计时器，所有进度数据都会自动保存到本地存储中。', 'ai', 342882657351860224, 341388430243610624, '2025-11-03 17:17:28', '2025-11-03 17:17:28', 0);
